Section 3.02 Equipment Standards and Specifications. All, equipment, materials
and Contractor Supplied Parts employed in any work performed by the Contractor in
connection with providing the Services shall be new and of good and workmanlike quality
and workmanship, equal to or better than the parts originally incorporated into each
System, shall not result in a limitation of the Warranties, and shall otherwise comply with
this Agreement.
